- u+s: (mode 4000) set user id on execution // new files in
       this directory will be owned by the directory owner
- g+s: (mode 2000) set group id on execution
- +t:  (mode 1000) set the sticky bit, directory contents may only
       be added, not renamed/deleted, except by owner of the files
- +X:  like +x, only affets dirs, in accordance with umask
- A=B: reset the permissions for A to B according to umask
